'''digibox''' (''plural'' '''digiboxes''')

#('''Digibox'''&reg;) a device marketed by [[w:British Sky Broadcasting|British Sky Broadcasting]] in the UK to enable home users to receive digital [[satellite]] [[television]] [[broadcast]]s.
#By tension, any [[digital]] [[TV]] [[receiver]] or [[decoder]] either [[terrestrial]], [[satellite]], or [[cable]], that is external to the TV.

